    <item>
      <title>华融第二名前高管因受贿被判处死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/a-second-ex-huarong-executive-sentenced-to-death-over-bribery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国以受贿罪判处中国华融国际控股有限公司一名前官员死刑，且不得缓期执行，这是中国当局多年来第二次罕见地判处一名高级金融高管死刑，同时当局加大了打击金融犯罪的力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/a-second-ex-huarong-executive-sentenced-to-death-over-bribery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:55:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ECP 将以每股 22 美元现金收购 Atlantica Sustainable</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/ecp-to-buy-atlantica-sustainable-for-22-per-share-in-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Energy Capital Partners 和联合投资者同意以每股 22 美元现金收购 Atlantica Sustainable Infrastructure Plc，从而获得遍布美国、欧洲、南美和非洲的可再生电力资产组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/ecp-to-buy-atlantica-sustainable-for-22-per-share-in-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:55:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛认为“略有波动”，但没有大的调整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-28/goldman-sachs-sees-bit-of-a-blip-but-no-big-correction-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛资产配置研究主管 Christian Mueller-Glissmann 表示，市场可能出现“一些波动”，但增长前景依然稳健。他告诉彭博电视台：“我们并不认为会出现大幅调整，但如果出现一些整合，我们肯定不会感到惊讶。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-28/goldman-sachs-sees-bit-of-a-blip-but-no-big-correction-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:54:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲顶级服装零售商 Pepkor 将支持巴西扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/top-africa-clothing-retailer-pepkor-to-bolster-brazil-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为非洲最大的服装零售商，Pepkor Holdings Ltd. 计划将其之前在巴西每年开设 50 家门店的目标提高近一倍，以推动南美洲的更快增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/top-africa-clothing-retailer-pepkor-to-bolster-brazil-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:45:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在债务拍卖热潮和通胀数据出现之前，国债保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/treasuries-steady-before-debt-auction-rush-and-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者期待一系列债务拍卖和美国通胀数据，美国国债小幅波动，两年期国债收益率保持在三周高点附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/treasuries-steady-before-debt-auction-rush-and-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:44:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赞比亚将迎来 6 月国际货币基金组织审查协议，因为默认退出已临近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/zambia-sees-latest-imf-review-sealed-in-june-with-funding-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚预计将于下个月完成与国际货币基金组织的第三次计划审查，因为这个铜资源丰富的国家最终确定了 5 亿美元的国际援助，以应对创纪录的干旱影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/zambia-sees-latest-imf-review-sealed-in-june-with-funding-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 07:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
